==English==
[[Category:Mammals]]
===Etymology===
From the Abenaki ''[[sakonkwa]].''
===Noun===
'''skunk''' (''plural'' '''skunks''')

# A small mammal [[native]] to North America, black with a white stripe and famous for emitting a [[noxious]] smell as a defensive measure.
# (''slang'') A type of strong [[marijuana]].
# (''slang'') A walkover victory in sports or board games, as when the opposing side is unable to score. Compare [[shutout]].
# Skinhead+Punk = skunk

